    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Sept 30 article about an organized crime scheme to sell forged paintings over Internet, which misstated the nationality of an artist</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on Sept. 30 about arrests in an organized crime scheme to sell forged paintings over the Internet included an erroneous reference from federal prosecutors to the nationality of Fernando Botero, one artist whose paintings were forged. He is Colombian, not Spanish.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An article on Sept. 30 about arrests in an organized crime scheme to sell forged paintings over the Internet included an erroneous reference from federal prosecutors to the nationality of Fernando Botero, one artist whose paintings were forged. He is Colombian, not Spanish.</p>
      </block>
